    <string name="welcome_title">Akwaaba</string>
    <string name="welcome_sovereignty">Wo keys.\nWo sika.\nWo tumi.</string>
    <string name="welcome_desc">Wo sika NTENA saa app yi mu. Ɛwɔ blockchain so, wo private keys na ɛkontrol.\n\nSaa app yi sie wo keys wɔ baabi a eye. Yentumi nkɔ wo sika ho.\n\nHwɛ: Tokens bi (USDC, USDT) wɔn a wɔyɛɛ no tumi bata. Sɛ wopɛ tumi a ɛboro so a, fa native ETH anaasɛ tokens a wɔnte hɔ wɔ centralized kwan so.</string>
    <string name="welcome_warning_title">Wo keys = Wo sika</string>
    <string name="welcome_warning_desc">Sɛ wohwere wo private keys anaasɛ woma obi bi a, wohwere wo sika nyinaa daa.\n\nƐkwan biara nni hɔ a wɔbɛfa so agye. Obiara nni hɔ a ɔbɛtumi aboa wo. Saa na nneɛma a wo dea tete te.\n\nHwɛ sɛ wuwie backup pa ma wo keys.</string>
    <string name="welcome_opensource">Open source software. Hwɛ mu, nngye nni.</string>
    <string name="welcome_start">Mate ase, ma yɛnhyɛ ase</string>

